Your boss ask for some specific unique style of code blocks ?
This can help you toggle it easily and you can keep your own habit by this way .
just try to use <F5> and <F6> to toggle !

if (a == b) {
        r = true ;
}

or :

if (a == b)
{
        r = true ;
}

